{"tid":2216436,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黑驚 消防 高下立見","createTime":"2020-09-24T16:05:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T18:02:15.000Z","uid":292865,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e13d4d9481589ee5ab468ca47d70895a5abc7d5","tid":2216436,"uid":292865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T16:05:42.000Z","msg":"榮瑞樓火警同層10歲愛犬燻黑喪命 女飼主衝入屋不果淚崩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3CiqRi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3CiqRi.jpg&h=f95e6eb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】沙田瀝源邨榮瑞樓一個單位下午4時發生三級火，火警在下午5時大致被救熄。消防表示，火警中有4人不適送院。據悉，消防起火單位內發現一名死者。<br />\n<br />\n消防在大廈中救出一隻狗，但當時該隻狗已經奄奄一息，消防員即場為狗進行心外壓及人工呼吸，但回天乏術。女狗主藍女士與親友得悉噩耗後情緒激動，送愛犬遺體上車時仍然難掩哀傷。女狗主透露，愛犬為10歲「囝囝」。<br />\n<br />\n居住起火同層單位的女狗主透露，火警發生時她正外出，得知發生火警隨即趕回家，但去到5樓時發現已經太大煙，無法入屋，估計可能屋內的煙太厲害奪命。直至火警救熄後，她交鎖匙給消防員，代為視察愛犬情況，發現牠全部毛已經燻黑，已無任何反應，經急救後依然無氣息，狗屍交由愛協帶走。<br />\n<br />\n她透露十分傷心，飼養了「囝囝」約10年，她悲嘆不知為何會火警，但火警屬意外，今次愛犬死亡她不怪任何人。雖然不捨，但亦無可奈何。"},{"pid":"02d49b797c414318ecab7df142ed132cbb8c7e14","tid":2216436,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T16:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69196b36beac92fe096692ce7c3612a16d746951","tid":2216436,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T16:23:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9846ff5c10b520b7050ebc42d2c227697ea8b4bc","tid":2216436,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T17:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />狗狗好慘"},{"pid":"0679407668e91a24bc008a08de2aa4ae0fb9014d","tid":2216436,"uid":49366,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T17:18:51.000Z","msg":"公屋養狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85d83e69669ee7bc2af1812825d0918ef95d276","tid":2216436,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T02:45:00.000Z","msg":"啲差狗 到唔到場都無撚分別"},{"pid":"d01fd023728cf40f95c8424cef605e17bb913e0d","tid":2216436,"uid":292865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c85d83e69669ee7bc2af1812825d0918ef95d276","tid":2216436,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T02:45:00.000Z","msg":"啲差狗 到唔到場都無撚分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T05:50:18.000Z","msg":"到場擋記者"},{"pid":"2335778c6e1340e826daf91e133436a3e4d07cd4","tid":2216436,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0679407668e91a24bc008a08de2aa4ae0fb9014d","tid":2216436,"uid":49366,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T17:18:51.000Z","msg":"公屋養狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/headache.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T06:00:17.000Z","msg":"有條件係可以申請架<br />\n<br />\n公共屋邨人口稠密，飼養狗隻可能會影響環境衞生及對租戶造成滋擾。香港房屋委員會(房委會)與租戶簽訂的租約已訂明，未經房委會書面同意，不得在出租單位飼養任何禽畜或牲口，包括狗隻。過往不少公屋租戶違規養狗，平均每年有數百戶在屋邨管理扣分制下被扣分。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">然而，如有視障或聽障租戶需飼養已受訓的引路犬，或個別租戶獲醫生或心理學家證明需以狗隻為伴作精神支柱而需要飼養的伴侶犬，在不造成滋擾的原則下，房委會會考慮酌情批准租戶飼養這些服務犬</span>。"},{"pid":"ae720c421a9faa8e53b2ad671837b9c26817ea66","tid":2216436,"uid":49366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2335778c6e1340e826daf91e133436a3e4d07cd4","tid":2216436,"uid":301820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0679407668e91a24bc008a08de2aa4ae0fb9014d","tid":2216436,"uid":49366